    <description>A utility tool to interact with XVNML files.</description>
    <releaseNotes>Pre-Release Version 1.0.2.1 for XVNML is now available! (September 2023 Update)

			Let's learn what's new, what's been patched, and everything in between.

			September 13th, 2023

			New
			* You are allowed to extend the use of pre-built tags using the Override Feature.
			* New Rich-Text Macro Controls. Those includes the following features:
			- Bold Macro (bold)
			- Bold End Macro (bold_end)
			- Color Macro (color::{string})
			- Color End Macro (color_end)
			- Emphasis Macro (emphasis)
			- Emphasis End Macro (emphasis_end)
			- Font Macro (font::{string})
			- Font End Macro (font_end)
			- Font Size Macro (size::{int})
			- Font Size End Macro (size_end)
			- Sprite Macro (sprite::{name})
			- StrikeThrough Macro (strikethrough)
			- Strike Through End Macro (strikethrough_end)
			- Style Macro (style::{string})
			- Underline Macro (underline)
			- Underline End Macro (underline_end)
			* Those were particularly added to support Unity, but should be compatible for any text box in any C# project (WPF, WinForm, UWP, etc.)

			Coming Soon
			* A new parameter for MacroCaches that allows to restrict where they are called.
			* The ability to pass through arguments for a macro defined in a MacroCache element, effectively creating your own custom macros inside XVNML itself as opposed to creating one via a C# Script.
			* A Unity package with XVNML integrated!
			* The use of the Variable Control Macros (declare, get, and set).</releaseNotes>
